AppendEntries

public AppendEntries(String source,
                     String destination,
                     long term,
                     long commitIndex,
                     long prevLogIndex,
                     long prevLogTerm,
                     @Nullable
                     Collection<LogEntry> entries)
Constructor.

Parameters:
source - unique id of the Raft server that generated the message
destination - unique id of the Raft server that is the intended recipient
term - election term in which the message was generated
commitIndex - index of the last LogEntry that the source server believes is committed
prevLogIndex - index of the LogEntry immediately before the first LogEntry in entries
prevLogTerm - election term in which the LogEntry at prevLogIndex was created
entries - sequence of monotonic, gapless, LogEntry instances with indices prevLogIndex + 1, prevLogIndex + 2 .. prevLogIndex + entries.count(). entries may be null if this AppendEntries message is a heartbeat
